snippet.title: Amber Heard at the L'Oréal Paris 'Women of Worth' on Time's Up movement
snippet.description:
On December 5th, Amber took part to the L'Oréal Paris 'Women of Worth' celebrations in New York. On the red carpet she spoke about the Time's Up movement and the huge gains it has made over these months.
